summary: AN UPDATEDESIGN FACTORS AFFECTING T & N DELIVERIES. W. Kelley provides an overview of the design factors that affect the delivery of T&N packages. We are happy to provide an explanation of these factors in this update. For more information, visit W Kelley's website.
